<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Invitation Accepted! - Barbershop</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .title {
            color: #059669;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .subtitle {
            color: #64748b;
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .success-box {
            background-color: #d1fae5;
            border-left: 4px solid #059669;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .coupon-box {
            background-color: #fef3c7;
            border: 2px dashed #f59e0b;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .coupon-code {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #d97706;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #059669;
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            color: #6b7280;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1 class="title">🎉 Your Invitation Was Accepted!</h1>
            <p class="subtitle">{{FriendName}} accepted your invitation</p>
        </div>

        <div class="success-box">
            <h2 style="color: #059669; margin-top: 0;">✅ Congratulations!</h2>
            <p style="font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 0;">
                <strong>{{FriendName}}</strong> accepted your invitation and now you both got <strong>1 month free</strong> on Barbershop!
            </p>
        </div>

        <p>Hello {{InviterName}}!</p>
        
        <p>Great news! <strong>{{FriendName}}</strong> accepted your invitation and joined Barbershop. As a thank you, you both got special benefits:</p>

        <div class="coupon-box">
            <h3 style="color: #d97706; margin-top: 0;">🎁 Your 1 Month Free Coupon</h3>
            <div class="coupon-code">{{CouponCode}}</div>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 0; color: #92400e;">
                Use this coupon on your next subscription renewal to get 1 month free!
            </p>
        </div>

        <div style="text-align: center;">
            <a href="{{AppName}}/dashboard" class="cta-button">
                🚀 Access Dashboard
            </a>
        </div>

        <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280;">
            <strong>How to use the coupon:</strong><br>
            1. Access your Barbershop account<br>
            2. Go to "Settings" > "Coupons"<br>
            3. Apply the code <strong>{{CouponCode}}</strong><br>
            4. The discount will be applied on the next billing
        </p>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>© 2024 {{AppName}}. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>Thank you for sharing Barbershop with your friends!</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 